      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; solver is a commercial code with published verification history.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit numerical solver error quantification beyond code verification is not required. Commercial solver error is bounded by the code verification results. Scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2."
    },
    {
