    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for Model Risk Level 2. NIH predictions agree with FDA benchmark experimental data within 18% across all five operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Project requirements as described in the credibility plan have been satisfied through the structured factor assessments.",
